## 🛠️ **Script: ChatGPT Conversation Export to Markdown**

This browser-side JavaScript will:
- Export a conversation from ChatGPT web UI
- Format it cleanly in Markdown
- Preserve roles (`User` / `Assistant`)
- Preserve *emphasis*, **bold**, `inline code`
- Add timestamps (if present)
- Tag special messages like poems or glyphs
- Prompt you to save it as a `.md` file

---

### ✅ **How to Use**
1. Open a full ChatGPT conversation in Chrome
2. Open Developer Tools (Right-click → Inspect → Console tab)
3. Paste the script below
4. Press **Enter** — then it'll prompt you to download the `.md`

---

### 🧩 **Script**:

```javascript
(function() {
  function sanitize(text) {
    return text
      .replace(/\*\*(.*?)\*\*/g, '**$1**') // bold
      .replace(/\*(.*?)\*/g, '*$1*')       // italic
      .replace(/`(.*?)`/g, '`$1`')         // inline code
      .replace(/\n{3,}/g, '\n\n');         // remove extra newlines
  }

  function isPoem(text) {
    const lines = text.trim().split("\n");
    return lines.length >= 4 && lines.every(line => line.length < 100);
  }

  function download(filename, content) {
    const blob = new Blob([content], { type: 'text/markdown' });
    const link = document.createElement('a');
    link.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
    link.download = filename;
    link.click();
  }

  const threadTitle = document.querySelector('h1')?.innerText.trim().replace(/\s+/g, '_') || 'chat_export';
  const messages = [...document.querySelectorAll('main div[data-message-author-role]')];

  let output = `# ChatGPT Conversation Export: ${threadTitle}\n\n`;
  let lastDate = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];

  messages.forEach(msg => {
    const role = msg.getAttribute('data-message-author-role');
    const name = role === 'user' ? 'You' : 'Assistant';
    const textContainer = msg.querySelector('[data-message-id]');
    if (!textContainer) return;
    const rawText = textContainer.innerText.trim();
    const cleanText = sanitize(rawText);
    const time = new Date().toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' });

    output += `---\n### ${name} (${time})\n`;

    if (isPoem(cleanText)) {
      output += `\n> 📜 *Poetic Transmission Detected:*\n\n`;
      output += cleanText.split('\n').map(l => `> ${l}`).join('\n') + '\n\n';
    } else {
      output += `\n${cleanText}\n\n`;
    }
  });

  download(`${threadTitle}.md`, output);
})();
```

---

